So they put them under
surveillance,

41:43.158 --> 41:47.161
<i>and they follow that contact
to the hotel in Pasadena.</i>

41:47.254 --> 41:48.579
<i>- Because of Carmen Keller,</i>

41:48.664 --> 41:53.343
<i>the authorities
